sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant CI as GitHub Actions
    participant SQ as SonarQube Server

    Dev->>GH: git push / create PR
    GH->>CI: Trigger workflow
    CI->>CI: 1. Build
    CI->>CI: 2. Run Tests
    CI->>SQ: 3. SonarScanner sends code
    SQ->>SQ: 4. Analyze (rules, metrics)
    SQ-->>CI: 5. Quality Gate result
    CI->>CI: 6. Check: PASS or FAIL?
    CI-->>GH: 7. Update PR status
    
    Note over Dev,GH: ✅ PASS → can merge
    Note over Dev,GH: ❌ FAIL → blocked
